<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="page-shell">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-hero">
      <div class="page-copy">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1>Built to make online shopping feel easier, calmer, and more open.</h1>
        <p>
          Rise N Reign is being shaped as a flexible online shop where customers can shop
          comfortably from home, discover what fits their lifestyle, and feel supported from the
          very first visit.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="founder-layout">
      <figure class="founder-portrait-card fade-up">
        <div class="founder-portrait-frame">
          <img
            src="/images/founder-matilda-karowal.jpg"
            alt="Matilda Karowal, founder of Rise N Reign"
            class="founder-portrait-photo"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="founder-image-note">
          <strong>Matilda Karowal</strong>
          <span>Founder of Rise N Reign</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <article class="founder-message-card fade-up fade-delay-1">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">Founder&apos;s Message</p>
        <h2>A note from Matilda Karowal</h2>
        <blockquote class="founder-quote">
          <p>
            I want my customers to experience easy and flexible online shopping, where they can
            shop comfortably from home without any problems.
          </p>
          <p>
            I have bigger plans for this online shop, but I believe this is just the beginning of
            something greater.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <p class="section-body">
          That message sits at the center of Rise N Reign. The goal is not only to offer products,
          but to create a smoother, more welcoming way for people to shop with confidence and ease.
        </p>
        <div class="founder-signoff">
          <strong>Matilda Karowal</strong>
          <span>Founder, Rise N Reign</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <article class="about-story-card fade-up">
      <p class="page-eyebrow">The Vision</p>
      <h2>What Rise N Reign is growing into</h2>
      <p class="section-body">
        This store is being built with everyday convenience in mind. Customers should be able to
        browse with ease, choose what they need without confusion, and feel comfortable shopping
        from wherever they are.
      </p>
      <p class="section-body">
        At the same time, the vision reaches further. Rise N Reign wants to grow into a stronger
        online space that supports discovery, trust, and a wider connection between thoughtful
        products and the people looking for them.
      </p>
    </article>

    <div class="page-grid">
      <article class="info-card about-info-card">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">Customer Experience</p>
        <h2>Shopping should feel simple</h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          The experience is meant to feel easy and flexible. Clear browsing, comfortable shopping
          from home, and a smoother path from discovery to ordering all matter here.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="info-card about-info-card">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">Community</p>
        <h2>Built to support more than one story</h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          Rise N Reign is also growing with a wider purpose in mind: making space for local makers,
          small businesses, and products that deserve a broader audience online.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="info-card about-info-card">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">Beginning</p>
        <h2>This is only the first step</h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          Bigger plans are already part of the vision. What exists today is the beginning of
          something that will continue to grow in depth, reach, and intention over time.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>
